quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,38,"Jokkumi diina baabiraa…ìe am …ìen: Ibraahiimaa e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba; ko kan woni diina bajjin…óingol Alla. Sellantaa men nde men kafidata e Alla go…ó…óum goo. Ko Kanko woni heeror…óo gootaagu. On tawhiidi e gom…óinal ko mi woni e mun min e baabiraa…ìe am …ìen, ko jeyaa…óum e …ìural Alla e dow amen nde O hawrindini men e …óum. Jeyaa…óum kadi e …ìural Makko e dow yim…ìe …ìen fow nde tawnoo O imminii Annabaa…ìe e ma…ì…ìe; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe yettatah Alla e neemaaji Makko …óin, ko yeddugol Mo …ìe wa…óata."
  12,39,"Refti Yuusufa yewti sukaa…ìe …ìen …ói…óo ka kaso o maakani …ìe: E ko rewugol rewetee…ói sertu…ói …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko rewugol Alla Gooto Mo alaa kafidii…óo On, On Foolu…óo tanaa Mun, Mo fooletaake?"
  12,40,"On alaa e rewde gaanin Alla, si wanaa in…óe …óe hikkaaki nokku, …óe innitir…óon onon e baabiraa…ìe mon rewetee…óe, …óe alah non huunde e ge…ìal ka reweede, Alla jippinanaali kon ko innitir…óon …óe hujja tinndinoowo sellugol …óe. √ëaawoore tagu ngun fow alanaa si wanaa Alla gooto On, wanah …óee in…óe …óe innitir…óon onon e baabiraa…ìe mon. Alla yamirii on nde bajjin…óinirton Mo dewal, O ha…ói on kafidugol Mo e go…ó…óum goo. Ko …óum woni diina √±ii…ìuka ka oo√±aare alaa e mu'un; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa …óum, ko …óum wa…ói si …ìe sirkannde Alla, …ìe rewa tagaa…ói goo."
  12,41,"Ko onon yo wondii…ìe am …ói…óo ka kaso! Yi'u…óo e mon on no hama inbu, o yaltay woni ka kaso, o yiltitoo e golle makko, o yarna laam…óo on. Oya yi'u…óo cobbal ngal ka hoore-mun colli no √±aama e maggal, ko waretee…óo fetee, colli …óin √±aama teewu hoore makko nden. Fiyaaku mo lanndi…óon fii mun on √±aawaama gasii. ∆äum ko wa…óay…óum feere alaa."
  12,42,"Yuusufu maakani on mo o sikki da…óay e ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo -onon woni yarnoowo laam…óo on-: Janto fii am ka laam…óo on, hino gasa ka o yaltina lam ka kaso. Seytaane yejjntini yarnoowo on jantagol fii Yuusufa ka laam…óo on. Yuusufa √±ii…ìiti ka kaso …ìaawo …óum, yoga e duu…ìi."
  12,43,"Laam…óo on wi'i: Min mi yi'ii e koy…óol na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói, na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin. Mi yi'ii kadi butaali jee…ói…ói kecce e yooru…óe jee…ói…ói. Ko onon yo mbatu dental, humpitee lam firo ngol koy…óol, si on laatike anndu…ìe firo koy…ói."